{
  "stem": "13469.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We weren't there for the liberation, which of course now is all the rage, the films, and [INAUDIBLE], and the speeches, and the horrible photographs, and films, and everything that everybody has seen about Belsen.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We missed it all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We've heard all about it kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when we left on the 10th, we now hear, we now know that the British army was about 25 miles from Belsen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I've-- when I've given my talks, especially to Rotary Clubs, there's always somebody who was in the British army who was first into Belsen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole British army has been to Belsen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they have, because the whole British army actually moved, swept through France, Belgium, Holland, Germany, and up toward Denmark.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were not allowed to go to Berlin, because Berlin was supposed to be for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was some agreement.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the whole British army moved up in that direction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they all came through Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all of them claim to have seen Belsen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And most of them have been there first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Got a chap living just down the road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He saw my article one day and rang me up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was one of the first in Belsen in the tanks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he didn't go in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He got to Belsen, to the gates, and he saw what was inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they carried on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were not allowed to stop, because it was a typhus area by that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the British army was very hesitant about going inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But what happened at the liberation is fairly well known to many people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I won't dwell on that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, the train was one of the best parts of our captivity, really, where Rudi came to the fore very much.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
